FBIS3-36850 "drsov028_d_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-028 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Feb 1994 Regional Affairs Emergency Fuel Situation in Kaliningrad Noted LD1002094094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0900 GMT 10 Feb 94 LD1002094094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] A special situation has been declared in Kaliningrad Oblast as of today in connection with an acute shortage of fuel resources. The shortage of fuel has been caused by the insolvency of enterprises that cannot pay suppliers. A headquarters has been set up under the head of administration to distribute the available fuel allocating it, first of all, to the vitally important industries.
